  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Part Time Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Hey you — yes, you!</strong></p><p>If you’re organised, detail-oriented, and can juggle multiple tabs like a pro (on your screen <em>and</em> in life), we’d love to meet you.</p><p>Whether you’re kickstarting your career or looking to sharpen your admin skills, this role gives you hands-on exposure to the insurance and finance industry, along with a supportive team, a positive environment, and clear opportunities to grow.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p>Liaise with clients in a friendly, professional manner</p><p>Handle documentation, submissions, and follow-ups</p><p>Keep digital and physical records organised and updated</p><p>Provide administrative support to the sales team</p><p><strong>You’ll Be a Great Fit If You…</strong></p><p>Are organised, responsible, and communicate clearly</p><p>Are comfortable with Microsoft Office (Canva is a bonus!)</p><p>Have prior admin or insurance experience — helpful but not required</p><p>Enjoy staying on top of tasks and checking things off your list</p><p>Are a positive, reliable team player</p><p><strong>What’s In It for You</strong></p><p>A genuinely supportive team that’s always ready to help</p><p>Real industry exposure and practical skills you’ll actually use</p><p>Clear pathways for long-term career progression</p><p>A chill yet professional work culture that values balance and teamwork</p><p>If you’re ready to learn, grow, and contribute to a team that cares, we’d love to hear from you.</p>",
